name: Rosemary-Roasted Potatoes
keywords: red potato, rosemary oil, side dish, vegan, vegetarian
recipeIngredient: 8 large red potatoes, cut into 1/2-inch cubes

recipeInstructions.text: Heat the oven to 450 degrees. Toss the potatoes with the rosemary oil and pepper and divide between 2 baking sheets. Roast until tender, shaking the pans occasionally, about 30 minutes. Toss with the salt and chopped rosemary and serve.
